column2: The leftmost column refers to the photo file name in each folder
The second column and the columns to its right logs its number. For example, 1049 means "DSC_1049.raw", 890 means "DSC_0890.raw"
altText is the alternative text that can be passed as the category parameter in the URL. (So category=0 is equivalent to category=qokjviw, which is bricks)
